OL,3,CTwo admit rioting following the deaths
OL,4,Cof boys in e-bike crash
OL,6,FTwo people have admitted rioting
OL,7,Ffollowing the deaths of two teenagers
OL,8,Fafter an e-bike crash in Cardiff.
OL,10,FJamie Jones, 24, and Lianna Tucker,
OL,11,F19, pleaded guilty to the charge of
OL,12,Friot in the Ely area of Cardiff in
OL,13,F2023.
OL,15,FUnrest followed the deaths of Kyrees
OL,16,FSullivan, 16, and Harvey Evans, 15, on
OL,17,Fthe evening of May 22 2023 when they
OL,18,Fcrashed on an e-bike minutes after
OL,19,FCCTV captured them being followed by a
OL,20,FSouth Wales Police van.
