OL,3,CTwo admit rioting following the deaths
OL,4,Cof boys in e-bike crash
OL,6,FLocal people and police at the scene
OL,7,Fclashed, leading to a riot that lasted
OL,8,Fseveral hours ` during which time
OL,9,Fdozens of officers were injured,
OL,10,Fproperty was damaged and cars were set
OL,11,Falight.
OL,13,FJones, from the Llanrumney area of
OL,14,FCardiff, and Tucker, from Ely,
OL,15,Fpreviously denied the offence, but
OL,16,Fchanged their plea at a hearing before
OL,17,FMerthyr Crown Court on Friday.
