OL,6,FJudge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke, the
OL,7,FRecorder of Cardiff, released the two
OL,8,Fon bail, with sentencing provisionally
OL,9,Fset for December 22.
OL,11,FMore than 40 people have been charged
OL,12,Fin connection with the incident.
OL,14,FDue to the number of defendants, the
OL,15,Fcourt has split the trial into three
OL,16,Fparts, with the first due to take
OL,17,Fplace on September 22.
